                     <interp inst="t18220417-45-person460" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was watching the premises, and saw two men on the roof bending something, and gave an alarm.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was locked out of my lodgings, and got on the roof seeing some one there.</p>
